{"tid":589141,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"今次補選睇到好多五毛扮本土派","createTime":"2018-03-11T16:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T12:41:51.000Z","uid":131158,"like":43,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"08585e0f2c5dfe98318600f54d379310f11f6d46","tid":589141,"uid":131158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:44:14.000Z","msg":"啲五毛而家好醒，扮本土派9嗡所謂焦土論，實質叫人讓路比建制<br />\n奇怪既係佢地只係針對新界東，大大力屌范國威，其他兩區又唔多提，差啲以為今次得咖哩范參選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解呢？因為佢同鄧家彪五五波嘛，建制拎到多一席已經賺晒<br />\n大家下屆睇路，而家啲五毛做晒功課，冇以前咁易捉<br />\n<br />\n你可以當我泛民打手，但話焦土果啲投完廢票冇下一步計劃就只係笑話一個，泛民有50%出賣你，但建制就100%，係咁簡單"},{"pid":"8498511e58e518bf8c9cb864cc9ba7637cdd7e6f","tid":589141,"uid":38904,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T17:00:21.000Z","msg":"但係班焦土撚話投彪彪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我重以為彪彪係本土派<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c488cc145d3b9ac60d0df36edd470df8542a1098","tid":589141,"uid":47027,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T17:23:49.000Z","msg":"好簡單，泛民上到去你都仲可以嗌下，建制上晒去都唔會講咁多，先整個坦克碌豬！"},{"pid":"7d371c1d2d822db120fddd5e496c15c156351803","tid":589141,"uid":126044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T18:01:27.000Z","msg":"冇野戇鳩得過網上鳩up焦土<br />\n<br />\n依家你唔係正式組織點撚樣玩策略"},{"pid":"04ef6ebd09bed0d3867de81fa4b5387fed30d790","tid":589141,"uid":131158,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T18:15:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但係班焦土撚話投彪彪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我重以為彪彪係本土派<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫人投廢票都明，投對家就真係r頭喇，所以而家啲五毛卧底太多<br />\n但我覺得唔好笑果啲人，先放下私怨，理性研究點增加非建制版圖先係正事，成日兩邊互串只會令建制漁人得利"},{"pid":"f8dd61b123bfd4ad3152e7ca70c3d3800c5023af","tid":589141,"uid":131158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T18:19:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇野戇鳩得過網上鳩up焦土<br />\n<br />\n依家你唔係正式組織點撚樣玩策略</blockquote><br />\n老實講，本土派已經元氣大傷，真係要用呢三年研究同準備點重整旗鼓，上次最高仕氣先得三四席,已經比人睇晒底牌"},{"pid":"4ac3e98c0e42501bbcf1270e3e811e86bdf735c1","tid":589141,"uid":33808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8dd61b123bfd4ad3152e7ca70c3d3800c5023af","tid":589141,"uid":131158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T18:19:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇野戇鳩得過網上鳩up焦土<br />\n<br />\n依家你唔係正式組織點撚樣玩策略</blockquote><br />\n老實講，本土派已經元氣大傷，真係要用呢三年研究同準備點重整旗鼓，上次最高仕氣先得三四席,已經比人睇晒底牌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T18:33:14.000Z","msg":"不如留tg一齊傾下"},{"pid":"c309be4cd5d733220e65820f4d46886c76694006","tid":589141,"uid":131158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T02:43:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冇野戇鳩得過網上鳩up焦土<br />\n<br />\n依家你唔係正式組織點撚樣玩策略</blockquote><br />\n老實講，本土派已經元氣大傷，真係要用呢三年研究同準備點重整旗鼓，上次最高仕氣先得三四席,已經比人睇晒底牌</blockquote>不如留tg一齊傾下</blockquote><br />\n冇咩好傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只要盡選民責任，去投票，<br />\n同下屆開多d post,唔好比五毛主導討論區風向就得"},{"pid":"40bf84e1ffe646db8b8791cb064